              "text": "[b]MELISSA[/b]\n\n\"Tom? Good, you answered.\"\n\n\"What you did was great and all, but we have a problem.\"\n\n\"That drone got a signal out before it went down.\"\n\n\"If that signal finishes routing, it is going to bring hell down on all of us.\"\n\n\"There is a relay beacon that routes local Vayrax-only transmissions through subspace. Hidden traffic. Local beacon hardware. Ugly, but reachable.\"\n\n\"I am sending you an access key now. If you leave immediately, you can still cut it off in time.\"",
