    "Chapter starts from hidden listener human_habitat_chapter_003_listener_001 installed by Chapter 002 final unlock.",
    "TAKE CALL is a masqueraded event_operations button; it opens Melissa's urgent call popup chain.",
    "Melissa's access handoff uses real item id vayrax_beacon_key via download_beacon_data so inventory receives the authored event item.",
    "ACCESS steps include requires_item vayrax_beacon_key for story/readability, but generic event_operations buttons do not enforce item checks in the current handler. The handoff step is the enforcement-safe part.",
    "Vayrax Interceptor event object points at authored enemy blueprint_id vayrax_drone_003.",
    "Relay is placed at Aster Local 07 / star_27_tier_1_local, sector [0, 3, -1], far enough from habitat for Auto Pilot travel pacing.",
    "Chapter 004 is not installed yet. Final step sets chapter_004_handoff_ready and completes Chapter 003.",
    "Chapter 004 activation listener is installed only by the Chapter 003 final COMPLETE button.",
    "Listener uses activate_event_on_range and starts human_station_chapter_004 at ch4_01_habitat_aftershock when the player is at the Human Station Habitat.",
    "Listener keeps spawn_on_step=manual_complete_only so it cannot be bulk-installed early."
